      <title>Sauce Barbecue maison</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/hobbies/cuisine/sauce-barbecue/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Jun 2025 22:21:00 +0200</pubDate><author>blog@ckevin.fr (Kevin)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/hobbies/cuisine/sauce-barbecue/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a id=&#34;figure--Sauce barbecue maison&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
